<p>The <code>@last</code> property returns TRUE if this is the last iteration.</p>

<h2>Basic Usage</h2>
<pre>{open}users{close}
  &lt;li&gt;{open}$name{close}&lt;/li&gt;
  {open}@last ? &lt;/ul&gt;{close}
{open}/users{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
<ul>
{users}
  <li>{$name}</li>
  {@last ? </ul>}
{/users}

<h2>Conditional Block</h2>
<pre>{open}colors{close}
  {open}@last{close}
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Last color: {open}$colors{close}&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
  {open}/@last{close}
{open}/colors{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
{colors}
  {@last}
    <p><b>Last color: {$colors}</b></p>
  {/@last}
{/colors}
